-spec find_high_access_employees(Access_times :: [[unicode:unicode_binary()]]) -> [unicode:unicode_binary()].
find_high_access_employees(Access_times) ->
    Access_times_int = [{binary_to_list(Name), list_to_integer(binary_to_list(Time))} || [Name, Time] <- Access_times],
    Sorted = lists:sort(fun({_, A}, {_, B}) -> A < B end, Access_times_int),
    Filtered = lists:foldl(fun({Name, Time}, Acc) ->
                               maps:update_with(Name, fun(Times) -> [Time | Times] end, [Time], Acc)
                           end, #{}, Sorted),
    High_access = maps:fold(fun(Name, Times, Acc) ->
                                Sorted_times = lists:sort(Times),
                                case lists:any(fun(Time) ->
                                                   case lists:dropwhile(fun(T) -> T < Time end, Sorted_times) of
                                                       [_, Second, Third | _] when Third - Time =< 59 -> true;
                                                       _ -> false
                                                   end
                                               end, Sorted_times) of
                                    true -> [Name | Acc];
                                    false -> Acc
                                end
                            end, [], Filtered),
    lists:sort(High_access).
